rComments: Very very helpful and very passionate. She explains stuff well

I've never had a TA as helpful and energetic as Alison is.  She's clearly passionate about Latin, and goes above and beyond to do anything and everything she can to help you out.  She's the reason I love Latin.

The class was completely fair. I got an A in the class, but I had to work fairly hard for the A. She will go above and beyond to make sure that you do as well as possible, just ask for help at any time. This class ended up being my favorite class first semester, she really is a great teacher who cares about Latin and her students.
